To set up lucene to run properly, you need to ensure the classpath is set:

use the following command:

export CLASSPATH=$CLASSPATH:./lucene-4.3.1/core/lucene-core-4.3.1.jar:./lucene-4.3.1/queryparser/lucene-queryparser-4.3.1.jar:./lucene-4.3.1/analysis/common/lucene-analyzers-commo\
n-4.3.1.jar:./lucene-4.3.1/demo/lucene-demo-4.3.1.jar:.   

